<a name='hSpriteSheets'></a>
>> Spritesheets
*Using Spritesheets for animated objects*
If your animated sprites are bundled inside sprite sheets, please look at the [[./data/fantomCX/examples/SpriteSheets/SheetAnim/SheetAnim.cxs|SheetAnim.cxs]] script.

*Texture atlas / Sprite sheets*
Sprite sheets are a great way to preserve video memory and also speed up the render process. To use texture atlas created by the tool [a http://www.codeandweb.com/texturepacker]TexturePacker[/a], check out the [[./data/fantomCX/examples/SpriteSheets/TexturePacker/TexturePacker.cxs|TexturePacker.cxs]] script.

