<a name='hText'></a>
>> Text
*FontMachine*
If you want to use FontMachine fonts, you don't need to do anything special: [[./data/fantomCX/examples/Text/FontMachine/FontMachine.cxs|FontMachine.cxs]].

*Multiline text*
To display multiline text, have a look at the [[./data/fantomCX/examples/Text/MultilineText/MultilineText.cxs|MultilineText.cxs]] script.

